<#63c0b20942a5a8f6cebb89f748b348a3> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/CMT_ADVIS_MERGER> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "false";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Kонсултативен kомитет за kонцентрациите"@bg, "Keskittymiä käsittelevä neuvoa-antava komitea"@fi, "Beratender Ausschuss für Unternehmenszusammenschlüsse"@de, "Padomdevēja komiteja uzņēmumu koncentrācijas jautājumos"@lv, "Comité consultivo de concentraciones"@es, "Det Rådgivende Udvalg for Kontrol med Fusioner og Virksomhedsovertagelser"@da, "Comitet consultativ în materie de concentrări"@ro, "Savjetodavnim odborom za koncentracije"@hr, "Advisory Committee on Concentrations"@en, "Svetovalnim odborom za koncentracije"@sl, "Poradný výbor pre koncentrácie"@sk, "Poradní výbor pro spojování"@cs, "Összefonódásokkal foglalkozó tanácsadó bizottság"@hu, "Συμβουλευτική επιτροπή συγκεντρώσεων"@el, "Adviescomité voor concentraties"@nl, "Kumitat konsultattiv dwar il-konċentrazzjonijiet"@mt, "Komitet Doradczy ds. Koncentracji"@pl, "Rådgivande kommittèn för företagskoncentrationer"@sv, "Koondumist käsitleva nõuandekomiteega"@et, "Comité consultatif en matière de concentrations"@fr, "Comité Consultivo em matéria de Concentrações"@pt, "Koncentracijų patariamasis komitetas"@lt, "An Coiste Comhairleach um Chomhchruinnithe"@ga, "Comitato consultivo in materia di concentrazioni"@it;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Committee, composed of representatives of the Member States, which is consulted by the Commission in antitrust and merger cases where such a consultation is foreseen. A preliminary draft decision by the Commission is submitted to, and discussed with, the advisory committee in question. The advisory committee issues an opinion, which shall be taken into account in the final Commission decision."@en, "Comité, composé de représentants des États membres, que la Commission consulte dans les affaires d’entente et de concentration, lorsque cette consultation est prévue. La Commission lui présente un avant-projet de décision et l’examine avec lui. Le comité consultatif émet un avis, qui doit être pris en compte dans la décision finale de la Commission."@fr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "CMT_ADVIS_MERGER"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0000775"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "CMT_ADVIS_MERGER"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/CMT_ADVIS_MERGER_1990_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "CMT_ADVIS_MERGER";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "CMT_ADVIS_MERGER";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "CMT_ADVIS_MERGER";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "1990-09-21";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "CMT_ADVIS_MERGER";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/EURUN>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#historyNote> "Alternative label: Advisory Committee on Mergers"@en
}
