    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Det europæiske videnskabeligt rådgivende organ om klimaændringer"@da, "Europeiska vetenskapliga rådgivande organet för klimatförändringar"@sv, "Kliimamuutusi käsitlev Euroopa teadusnõukogu"@et, "Consejo Científico Consultivo Europeo sobre Cambio Climático"@es, "Consiliul științific consultativ european privind schimbările climatice"@ro, "Eiropas Zinātniskā konsultatīvā padome klimata pārmaiņu jautājumos"@lv, "Европейски научен консултативен съвет по изменението на климата"@bg, "Bord Konsultattiv Xjentifiku Ewropew dwar it-Tibdil fil-Klima"@mt, "Evropský vědecký poradní výbor pro změnu klimatu"@cs, "Europäischer Wissenschaftlicher Beirat für Klimawandel"@de, "European Scientific Advisory Board on Climate Change"@en, "Az éghajlatváltozással foglalkozó európai tudományos tanácsadó testület"@hu, "Conseil scientifique consultatif européen sur le changement climatique"@fr, "Europejski naukowy komitet doradczy ds. zmiany klimatu"@pl, "Europos mokslo patariamoji taryba klimato kaitos klausimais"@lt, "Európska vedecká poradná rada pre zmenu klímy"@sk, "Europese wetenschappelijke adviesraad inzake klimaatverandering"@nl, "Comitato consultivo scientifico europeo sui cambiamenti climatici"@it, "Bord Comhairleach Eolaíoch Eorpach um an Athrú Aeráide"@ga, "Conselho Consultivo Científico Europeu sobre as Alterações Climáticas"@pt, "Ευρωπαϊκή Επιστημονική Συμβουλευτική Επιτροπή για την Κλιματική Αλλαγή"@el, "Evropski znanstveni svetovalni odbor za podnebne spremembe"@sl, "Europski znanstveni savjetodavni odbor za klimatske promjene"@hr, "Ilmastonmuutosta käsittelevä eurooppalainen tieteellinen neuvottelukunta"@fi;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "EU body that provides independent scientific advice and produces reports on EU measures, climate targets and indicative greenhouse gas budgets and their coherence with the European Climate Law and the EU’s international commitments under the Paris Agreement; it is composed of 15 senior scientific experts covering a broad range of relevant disciplines and supported in its work by a secretariat hosted by the EEA"@en;
