    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "cooperation network between the European Commission, the European Labour Authority, the national public and other admitted employment services – in all the European Union countries, Iceland, Liechtenstein, Norway and Switzerland – to facilitate the free movement of workers, by providing information and employment support services to workers and employers, and by enhancing cooperation and information exchange between its member organisations"@en;
