    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "EU:n edustustot ja toimistot"@fi, "EU-delegaties en -bureaus"@nl, "Delegatury i biura UE"@pl, "EU’s delegationer og kontorer"@da, "Uniós küldöttségek és hivatalok"@hu, "Αντιπροσωπείες και γραφεία της ΕΕ"@el, "Делегации и служби на ЕС"@bg, "Delegacije i uredi EU-a"@hr, "Toscaireachtaí agus Oifigí an Aontais Eorpaigh"@ga, "Delegações e gabinetes da UE"@pt, "Delegazioni e uffici dell’UE"@it, "Delegacije in uradi EU"@sl, "EU-delegationer och EU-kontor"@sv, "Delegații și birouri ale UE"@ro, "Délégations et bureaux de l’UE"@fr, "Delegazzjonijiet u Uffiċċji tal-UE"@mt, "Delegácie a úrady EÚ"@sk, "EU-Delegationen und -Vertretungen"@de, "EU Delegations and Offices"@en, "ES delegācijas un biroji"@lv, "Delegaciones y oficinas de la UE"@es, "Delegací a zastoupení EU"@cs, "ELi delegatsioonid ja bürood"@et, "ES delegacijos ir biurai"@lt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The European External Action Service is responsible for EU Delegations and Offices operating around the world, representing the European Union and its citizens globally. The EU Delegations play a key role in presenting, explaining and implementing EU’s foreign policies. They also analyse and report on the policies and developments of their host countries and conduct negotiations in accordance with given mandates."@en;
