    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "EISMEA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-mapped-code> _:b1798_b1797_b1796_df_15_507, _:b1798_b1797_b1796_df_15_508, _:b1798_b1797_b1796_df_15_509, _:b1798_b1797_b1796_df_15_510;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COM>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#historyNote> "According to the Commission Implementing Decision (EU) 2021/173 of 12 February 2021 (http://data.europa.eu/eli/dec_impl/2021/173/oj), the European Innovation Council and SMEs Executive Agency is established from 1 April 2021 until 31 December 2028 and it succeeds and replaces the Executive Agency for Small and Medium-sized Enterprises."@en.
