<#1ac0b5bbe52a43de6ad2a50435d0de68> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/HADEA> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "false";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Agência de Execução Europeia da Saúde e do Digital"@pt, "Europejska Agencja Wykonawcza ds. Zdrowia i Cyfryzacji"@pl, "Europska izvršna agencija za zdravlje i digitalno gospodarstvo"@hr, "Agence exécutive européenne pour la santé et le numérique"@fr, "L-Aġenzija Eżekuttiva Ewropea għas-Saħħa u għall-Qasam Diġitali"@mt, "Agenția Executivă Europeană pentru Domeniile Sănătății și Digital"@ro, "Det Europæiske Forvaltningsorgan for Sundhed og det Digitale Område"@da, "Euroopa Tervishoiu ja Digitaalvaldkonna Rakendusamet"@et, "Agencia Ejecutiva Europea en los ámbitos de la Salud y Digital"@es, "Evropska izvajalska agencija za zdravje in digitalno tehnologijo"@sl, "Europeiska genomförandeorganet för hälsofrågor och digitala frågor"@sv, "Europees Uitvoerend Agentschap voor gezondheid en digitaal beleid"@nl, "Evropská výkonná agentura pro zdraví a digitální oblast"@cs, "Europäische Exekutivagentur für Gesundheit und Digitales"@de, "Európska výkonná agentúra pre zdravie a digitalizáciu"@sk, "European Health and Digital Executive Agency"@en, "Euroopan terveys- ja digitaaliasioiden toimeenpanovirasto"@fi, "An Ghníomhaireacht Feidhmiúcháin Eorpach um an tSláinte agus an Digitiú"@ga, "Európai Egészségügyi és Digitális Végrehajtó Ügynökség"@hu, "Ευρωπαϊκός Εκτελεστικός Οργανισμός για την Υγεία και τον Ψηφιακό τομέα"@el, "Europos sveikatos ir skaitmeninės ekonomikos vykdomoji įstaiga"@lv, "Agenzia esecutiva europea per la salute e il digitale"@it, "Европейска изпълнителна агенция за здравеопазването и цифровизацията"@bg, "Eiropas Veselības un digitālā izpildaģentūra"@lt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The European Health and Digital Executive Agency is entrusted with the implementation of the following (parts of) Union programmes: EU4Health programme; Horizon Europe: Pillar II, Cluster 1: Health; Single Market Programme: Food safety: health for humans, animals and plants along the food chain and better training for safer food; Digital Europe Programme; Connecting Europe Facility: Digital; Horizon Europe: Pillar II, Cluster 4: Digital, industry and space, as well as with the implementation of the legacy of the following (parts of) Union programmes: Horizon 2020: Part III: Societal Challenge 1: Health, demographic change and well-being; Connecting Europe Facility: Telecom; Horizon 2020: Part II: specific objective ‘Leadership in enabling and industrial technologies (LEIT)’ – ICT, NMBP, space; Horizon 2020: Part III: Societal challenge 5: Climate action, Environment, resource efficiency and raw materials; FP7: The theme ‘space’ of the specific programme cooperation of the Seventh Framework Programme; the Common financial framework in the area of food and feed safety including Better training for safer food; the third Programme for the Union’s action in the field of health (2014-2020)"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "HADEA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#PUB_CORP>, "95242"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#ISBN_RG>, "HW"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#OP_CAT>, "HADEA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>, "HADEA_CRF_250215"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>, "10.2925"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#DOI_P>, "HADEA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001632"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "HADEA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "HaDEA"@nl, "HaDEA"@it, "HaDEA"@ro, "HaDEA"@lv, "HaDEA"@el, "HaDEA"@pt, "HaDEA"@sk, "HaDEA"@de, "HaDEA"@et, "HaDEA"@hu, "HaDEA"@sv, "HaDEA"@en, "HaDEA"@sl, "HaDEA"@ga, "HaDEA"@fi, "HaDEA"@cs, "HaDEA"@bg, "HaDEA"@hr, "HaDEA"@fr, "HaDEA"@es, "HaDEA"@da, "HaDEA"@pl, "HaDEA"@lt, "HaDEA"@mt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/HADEA_2021_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "HADEA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/op-code> "HADEA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-code> "HADEA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/start.use> "2021-02-16";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/authority-code> "HADEA";
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/op-mapped-code> _:b1810_b1809_b1808_df_15_515, _:b1810_b1809_b1808_df_15_516, _:b1810_b1809_b1808_df_15_517;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#broader> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/COM>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#historyNote> "According to the Commission Implementing Decision (EU) 2021/173 of 12 February 2021 (http://data.europa.eu/eli/dec_impl/2021/173/oj), the European Health and Digital Executive Agency is established from 16 February 2021 until 31 December 2028."@en.
_:b1810_b1809_b1808_df_15_515 a <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/MappedCode>;
